This is truly a 4 fork recipe: big flavors, ease of preparation, and high in nutrition. I used red cabbage and spinach in the slaw since that's what I had on hand, and one serrano pepper since the store didn't have red jalapenos. Wonderful sweet/spicy combo and the grilling time for the flank steak was right on target. Will make again-a new summer favorite

