Rating: 4
This was great. Because I wasn't going to cook it the day I marinated it, I put it in a bag in the freezer, which allows the marination to continue in slow motion. When I pulled it out 2 days later, it grilled up perfectly & very tastily. Served it with a chopped salad of grilled sweet onion, tomato & sugar snap peas. Will make it again this summer for sure.

